{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Kemotaku&quot; is a brand new card game mixed with puzzle, deck building and tower-defence.<br>You can choose 4 main characters, and the game features a wide variety of animal cards, skills, and items.<br>Enjoy deep gaming experiences with your own style.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/main.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc36Defend your town from attacking enemies!\ud83d\udc31</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To successfully defend your town, your allies' power must exceed the enemies' power.<br>You can gain power using cards, skills, and items.<br>Stand up to attacking enemies and keep up your health points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e1.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc3cStack animal cards to boost your power!\ud83d\udc3b</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each animal card comes with fruits, and you can stack them if their fruits match. <br>Each time you stack cards, The power is boosted up and you can defeat high-power enemies. <br>And as your trust levels increase, more powerful animals can join the battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e2.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc3aMatch fruits and trigger skills!\ud83d\udc37</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The 4 main characters have their own skills. <br>When animal cards are played and fruits match, skills are activated.<br>Triggering skills is very important to beat the game.<br>There are 48 skills per character and you can build your own skill deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e3.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc35Fresh gaming experience every time!\ud83d\udc39</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many enemies and bosses against you.<br>Every boss has strong skills and use them every turn.<br>If you can't deal with them well, you'll be defeated.<br>And the game features many events, items and a card upgrading system.<br>You can enjoy it again and again with fresh feelings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e4.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e5.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070040/extras/e6.jpg?t=1735888706\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc28Human Translations!\ud83d\udc27</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I translated all game texts from Japanese to English by myself, not machine translations.<br>If you find any weird parts, let me know.<br>I will fix it as soon as possible.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The First Step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3070040/68d97c0e0945a958a8efc789c80ecc589cde30d7.jpg"},{"name":"The Courage to Be Disliked","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3070040/cdd49b4f2e4893883dbe163d0ce5d1f204a73e78.jpg"},{"name":"Mission Completed!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3070040/d3e62b0242b3a0616ea9f043ac6033138b186fa6.jpg"},{"name":"You're the Hero!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3070040/a38d76ae1d78f530d4c4a1d9f492008b978869d4.jpg"},{"name":"Call the Police!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3070040/3b02b4effef639de